ml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WooCommerce Shipping\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://wedevs.com/?p=120036\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:526:\"<p>Shipping is one of the essential factors of completing an order from a WooCoomerce e-store. It is the free shipping that&#8230; </p>\n<p class=\"read-more\"><a class=\"btns\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/\">Continue reading &#8594;</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/\">WooCommerce Shipping Plugins For Dokan Multivendor Marketplace</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Tarun Sikder\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17262:\"<p>Shipping is one of the essential factors of completing an order from a <strong>WooCoomerce e-store</strong>. It is the free shipping that attracts customer the most. In many cases, the price attached to shipping deal affects the decision of customer buying that product. If the cost of shipping is higher then it normally <strong>discourages</strong> a customer to get that product from that particular site.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-120036\"></span></p>\n<p>So, therefore, every site requires a firm and convenient shipping policy. And in order to maintain that policy, you need to have comprehensive WooCommerce shipping plugin that would effectively deal your <strong>shipping regularities</strong> better. This would make the customer come to your site over and over again.</p>\n<p>Don\'t you want to improve the WooCommerce shipping <strong>service</strong> of your e-store?</p>\n<p>The answer should be easy right. So here are some of the most efficient WooCommerce shipping plugin for Dokan that can effectively enhance the <strong>shipping service</strong>.</p>\n<h2 class=\"plugin-title\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/fedex-woocommerce-shipping-method/\">FedEx WooCommerce Shipping Method Plugin</a></h2>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"120364\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/fedex-shipping-plugin-image/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1395,445\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"FedEx shipping plugin image\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-300x96.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-1024x327.jpg\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-120364 size-full\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image.jpg\" alt=\"FedEx WooCommerce Shipping Plugin\" width=\"1395\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image.jpg 1395w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-300x96.jpg 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-768x245.jpg 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-1024x327.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1395px) 100vw, 1395px\" /></p>\n<p>Well, the plugin is developed by <a href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/?utm_campaign=Dokan-shipping&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_source=wedevs\">XAdapter</a> who is one of the pioneers in the business of creating e-commerce extensions.</p>\n<p>Now we all know how <strong>popular</strong> FedEx is for their shipping services worldwide. But when you want to use the same standard of shipping service with your WooCoomerce site then you need to install and activate this plugin in <strong>DOKAN</strong>.</p>\n<p>This is a plugin that helps process the shipping of products in a WooCommerce based<strong> e-store</strong> through FedEx. The plugin helps its user to get the detail <strong>shipping rates</strong> based on the product\'s weight, location, and other related details.</p>\n<p>This extension to WooCommerce e-store brings an effective yet a <strong>powerful e-commerce shop</strong> to its customers. What makes it even more special is its ability to automatically identify boxes to pack the items and enable tracking.</p>\n<p>It provides multiple vendors to sell their products through a catalog keeping the facility to ship anywhere through a trusted carrier like FedEx. This plugin is approved and endorsed by <strong>FedEx International (US) Ltd</strong>.</p>\n<h3>How It Works</h3>\n<p>After Installing this plugin with WooCoomerce for Dokan, you will require to input the FedEx account details in order to use your <strong>negotiated</strong> rates. Before placing any order a customer gets to see the FedEx shipping rate based on the product that they have added to the cart.</p>\n<p>Within your WooCommerce order page, you then will have to Pay Postage, Print Label and Generate Tracking info for the goods to be shipped<strong> correctly</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Using the Plugin</h3>\n<p>Here is how you can setup &amp; use this WooCommerce FedEx Shipping plugin for Dokan</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'390\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/pU5D04agO6c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></div>\n<h3>Some Premium features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Print shipping label with postage.</li>\n<li>Automatic shipment tracking while generating the label.</li>\n<li>Weight-based packing &amp; box packing.</li>\n<li>Change the name of shipping services and add handling costs.</li>\n<li>CoD, Third party payer, FedEx LTL Freight &amp; Many more options.</li>\n<li>Timely compatibility updates and bug fixes.</li>\n<li>Premium support!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/fedex-woocommerce-shipping-method//\">Download the WooCommerce FedEx Shipping plugin→</a></strong></p>\n<h2 class=\"plugin-title\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/dhl-woocommerce-shipping-method/\">DHL WooCommerce Shipping Method Plugin</a></h2>\n<h2><img data-attachment-id=\"120365\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/dhl-shipping-plugin-image/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1402,455\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"DHL shipping Plugin image\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-300x97.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-1024x332.jpg\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-120365 size-full\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image.jpg\" alt=\"DHL WooCommerce Shipping plugin\" width=\"1402\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image.jpg 1402w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-300x97.jpg 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-768x249.jpg 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-1024x332.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1402px) 100vw, 1402px\" /></h2>\n<p>DHL is another popular <strong>shipping service</strong> platform from XAdapter that is loved by millions all over the world. And in the same way as FedEx, this shipping plugin also helps its user to process the shipping of their product in a WooCommerce site <strong>fast &amp; easy.</strong></p>\n<p>This is a plugin allows a customer to buy from multiple vendors in the same order and ship it through <strong>DHL courier service</strong>.</p>\n<p>The plugin helps <strong>automate</strong> the process of shipping providing DHL express service. It shows the accurate rate of shipping that is preset for the different locations before getting to the cart and checkout page in your <strong>WooCommerce store</strong>.</p>\n<p>This process also enables the tracking of shipment including automatic product <strong>packaging</strong> into boxes displaying the print label within WooCommerce. But this plugin only works for countries where the DHL Express service is <strong>available</strong>. And the whole process and this WooCommerce Shipping plugin have been verified &amp; by the <strong>DHL International (UK) Ltd</strong>.</p>\n<h3>How It Works</h3>\n<p>In the same way as FedEx, you need to install and activate the WooCommerce <strong>DHL plugin</strong> for Dokan by putting in the DHL account details, and enabling the <strong>DHL Express/Paket shipping</strong> method for WooCommerce. Since the <strong>shipping rates</strong> change based on the number and type of product you have carted before placing the order, hence it is essential to set the <strong>rate</strong> for shipping accordingly.</p>\n<p>Make necessary<strong> adjustment</strong> in the settings page and then Print Label, Generate Tracking info and Pay Postage within the <strong>WooCommerce order page</strong>. This will let you ship the product to the <strong>desired destination</strong> without any trouble.</p>\n<h3><strong>Using the</strong> plugin</h3>\n<div class=\"porto-separator tall\">\n<div class=\"divider align_center divider-primary\"> Here is how you can setup &amp; use the WooCommerce DHL Express plugin for Dokan.</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'390\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/PBCx1qLIccI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></div>\n<h3>Some Premium Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Print shipping label with Postage.</li>\n<li>Return Label.</li>\n<li>Commercial Invoice.</li>\n<li>Archive Air Waybill.</li>\n<li>Create &amp; Delete shipments in Bulk.</li>\n<li>Use the paperless trade feature and get a commercial invoice from DHL.</li>\n<li>Auto Shipment Tracking: Tracking info will be available to the customer while generating the label.</li>\n<li>Box packing with DHL boxes and Custom boxes.</li>\n<li>Enable/disable, edit the names of services and add handling costs to shipping services.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/dhl-woocommerce-shipping-method/\">Download the WooCommerce DHL Shipping plugin→</a></strong></p>\n<h2 class=\"plugin-title\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ups-woocommerce-shipping-method/\">UPS WooCommerce Shipping Method Plugin</a></h2>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"123041\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/ups-plugin-logo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/UPS-Plugin-logo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1402,450\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"UPS Plugin logo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/UPS-Plugin-logo-300x96.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/UPS-Plugin-logo-1024x329.jpg\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-123041 size-full\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/UPS-Plugin-logo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1402\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/UPS-Plugin-logo.jpg 1402w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/UPS-Plugin-logo-300x96.jpg 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/UPS-Plugin-logo-768x247.jpg 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/UPS-Plugin-logo-1024x329.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1402px) 100vw, 1402px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This is another wonderful shipping plugin to come out from Xadapter for WooCommerce. This plugin helps make the WooCommerce store user’s shipping method totally automated. With your WooCommerce store, this plugin shows real-time rates in carts/check out page, postage payment &amp; print label.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In case of both domestic &amp; international shipping, the plugin fetches rates from your UPS account based on the parcel’s size, weight &amp; shipping destinations. A customer can choose from the list of rates based on the postal codes and other related product measures.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Not only the plugin automatically choose boxes and initiate tracking of the shipping product but it also provides you the international prices of shipping services.Choose the way you want your parcel to be packed &amp; shipped. Not just that, with this plugin you get to edit the names, add costs and enable/disable the services very easily. You always feel in total control of your shipping method with this plugin.      </span></p>\n<h3><b>How It</b> Works</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Just like the other two shipping plugins above, UPS shipping plugin for WooCommerce is compatible with Dokan Multivendor Marketplace. So at first, you will be required to install and activate both the plugin in your WordPress.  </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Simply setup Dokan Multivendor plugin and configure the commissions to allow the vendors to directly register for it. Based weights, sizes of the parcel UPS then calculates the shipping price once the vendor uploads and configure their product.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">After that create shipment order by choosing the parcel packing method to automatically send labels to your vendors. Once checkout is done, the plugin shares its tracking details for the customers, enabling the vendors to manage their product reviews.       </span></p>\n<h3><b>Using</b> the<b> plugin</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Here is how you can setup and use this shipping plugin with WooCommerce for Dokan Multivendor.</span></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'390\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/Yyb7aNkgMZ4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></div>\n<h3><b>Some Premium Features</b></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Shipping label printing with postage.</li>\n<li>In-built live shipping rate in carts &amp; checkouts.</li>\n<li>Auto-shipment tracking while generating the shipping label.</li>\n<li>Parcel with weight-based packing.</li>\n<li>Enable/disable, edit the names of, and add costs to shipping services.</li>\n<li>Prompt compatibility updates &amp; bug fixes.</li>\n<li>Full range of freight services.</li>\n<li>Priority premium support.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ups-woocommerce-shipping-method/\">Download the UPS WooCommerce Shipping plugin→</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Observations</h2>\n<p>If you are selling physical goods then shipping is one of the<strong> basic necessity</strong> in your business plan. Keeping the cost of shipping at a reasonable range would<strong> boost up</strong> your conversion for sure. Not just that it would also change the <strong>perception</strong> of your e-store if you <strong>momentarily</strong> take off the burden of shipping cost from customers. It will definitely <strong>increase</strong> the number of order from your e-shop.</p>\n<h2>Concluding Words</h2>\n<p>If you are using WooCommerce with Dokan then you will definitely find this post<strong> useful</strong>. Our sole intention of this write up was to inform you about the<strong> necessity</strong> and use case of a <strong>powerful shipping plugin</strong> for Dokan to improve your WooCommerce website performance.</p>\n<p>So we hope you have <strong>enjoyed</strong> this post and found the use case of these valid WooCoommece shipping plugin for Dokan useful in some way.</p>\n<p>And if you are using WordPress and thinking about starting up a <strong>multivendor store</strong> on your own, then you may want to &#8211;</p>\n<p><strong><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\" href=\"http://dokandemo.wedevs.com/my-account/\">Try The Dokan Multivendor Marketplace Demo→</a></strong></p>\n<p>Do leave a comment if you have any <strong>queries</strong> regarding these shipping plugins for<strong> Dokan</strong>. We would be more than happy to assist you any way possible.</p>\n\n<div style=\"display: block !important; margin:0 !important; padding: 0 !important\" id=\"wpsclp_locker_post_end_element\"></div><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/\">WooCommerce Shipping Plugins For Dokan Multivendor Marketplace</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"120036\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8: